Some good resorces form where I learnt and took alot: 

1. http://page.math.tu-berlin.de/~kant/teaching/hess/krypto-ws2006/des.htm

2. Applied Cryptography, Second Edition: Protocols, Algorthms, and Source Code in C by Bruce Schneier

3. Introduction to Cryptography By Christof Paar (Video Tutorial)

4. Crypto I and Crypto II (Which are the online courses offered by Dan Boneh, professor of Stanford University in coursera)
